Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: c2c.recipe.cssmin
Version: 0.6
Summary: A buildout recipe to merge and compress css files
Home-page: https://github.com/camptocamp/c2c.recipe.cssmin
Author: Frederic Junod
Author-email: frederic.junod@camptocamp.com
License: MIT License
Description: =================
        c2c.recipe.cssmin
        =================
        
        Requirements
        ------------
        Requires zc.buildout and `cssmin <http://pypi.python.org/pypi/cssmin>`_
        
        Usage
        -----
        Create a buildout.cfg file which contains the following::
        
            [buildout]
            parts = cssmin
        
            [cssmin]
            recipe = c2c.recipe.cssmin
            input = foo/bar/file1.css
                    foo/bar/file2.css
                    foo/baz/file3.css
            output = foo/build/output.min.css
            compress = true
        
        Path are relative to the buildout directory, absolute path are also allowed.
        
